query:
SELECT a.user_id, a.storage_host_id, a.redeemed_at, a.authorized_amount 
                FROM storage_grants a
                WHERE a.redeemed_at IN (
                    SELECT MAX(b.redeemed_at)
                    FROM storage_grants b
                    WHERE a.user_id = b.user_id
                )
                GROUP BY a.id;
